restore all new cards description: You can restore all new cards associated with this box. The box itself cannot be restored as it is special and always present on the shelf.
restore all learnt cards description: You can restore all learnt cards associated with this box. The box itself cannot be restored as it is special and always present on the shelf.
remove all new cards description: You can remove all new cards associated with this box. The box itself cannot be removed as it is special and always present on the shelf.
remove all learnt cards description: You can remove all learnt cards associated with this box. The box itself cannot be removed as it is special and always present on the shelf.
